### Children — CRUD for child profiles and avatar upload

### Create a child — copy id from response into http-client.env.json as childId
### gender: Boy | Girl
POST {{host}}/api/children
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Emma",
  "age": 8,
  "gender": "Girl",
  "avatarEmoji": "👧"
}

###

### List all children in my family
GET {{host}}/api/children
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get a specific child
GET {{host}}/api/children/{{childId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update a child
PUT {{host}}/api/children/{{childId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Emma",
  "age": 9,
  "gender": "Girl",
  "avatarEmoji": "👧"
}

###

### Delete a child
DELETE {{host}}/api/children/{{childId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
